CatDescriptText: image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Lounging Model - Christine Sumpter, one of the D.I. models, lounges casually in beach attire on the "sands" of the Press Club during last Sunday's review."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Christine Sumpter wearing light colored bathing suit, posed in folding chair in home of Gloria Grate preparing for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue at the Press Club in the Hotel Sherwyn
